Package chessosisnbproject.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSS
    Class for globally available Constant Square Set data.
    Move
    Move objects represent possible moves in a particular position.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Colour
    A simple enum type for representing piece and square color as well as who's turn it is to move.
    Direction
    A simple enum type for representing directions on the board.
    Piece
    An enum type that represents the 12 distinct chess pieces.
    PieceType
    Represents the six piece types available in chess.
    Square
    Enum type Square makes it possible to treat the 64 squares of the chessboard as a distinct data type.
